column5: Went out on friends boat this A.M for some staging kings. Was thinking bluezone but with the wind prediction didn't want a see a rouge wave the Aaron S was talkng about in his thread. A bit slow with just two hits and one landed. Got pretty choppy so we called it a day.Got some practice for the fish off next saturday.
nice fish, congrats and better safe than sorry
Thats one Huge Salmon, How much did it weight?
Wow, nice salmon.  Turning dark already I see.  Joey
It was 24 pounds on the dot. It's was the darkest fish I've seen this year. Next big rain should bring them up the river.
Wow now thats a fat Salmon.  MTP
Thanks guys, hopfully we can get a heavy one like that tomorrow.
nice fish man, congrats. cant wait to get out on lake o myself....
